{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen Satz zur AfD-Fraktion: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach Ihrer Vorstellung sollen sich die Hochschulen in Zukunft wahrscheinlich nur noch f\u00fcr wei\u00dfe wohlhabende M\u00e4nner \u00f6ffnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ich habe ganz gut zugeh\u00f6rt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Eindruck konnte man ziemlich deutlich bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.440", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.280", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie das hier so deutlich ausgesprochen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Studierenden werden ihre Schl\u00fcsse daraus ziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt aber zum Thema: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das BAf\u00f6G war eine der wirklich gro\u00dfen Errungenschaften der sozial-liberalen Koalition unter Willy Brandt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.920", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Endlich sollte damit Schluss sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.360", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nur Kinder aus wohlhabenden Familien studieren und dass der soziale Status eben auch \u00fcber die Bildung einfach vererbt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das BAf\u00f6G war wirklich eines der Instrumente f\u00fcr Chancengleichheit und eine gerechtere Gesellschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine absolut wunderbare Erfindung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "knapp 50\u00a0Jahre nach Einf\u00fchrung des BAf\u00f6G, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die soziale Spaltung in der weiterf\u00fchrenden Bildung praktisch wieder auf dem Niveau von 1970 angekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.080", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist die ganz bittere Wahrheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist ein ziemlicher Skandal f\u00fcr ein so reiches Land wie Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Anteil der Studierenden aus Haushalten mit formal niedrigem Bildungsstand liegt bei nur 12\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1991 waren es noch doppelt so viele, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daran wird doch wirklich klar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.360", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie selektiv das Bildungssystem wieder geworden ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.280", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sozialer Aufstieg durch Bildung findet \u00fcber das BAf\u00f6G de facto nicht mehr statt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daf\u00fcr tragen Sie die Verantwortung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen der alten und der neuen Gro\u00dfen Koalition."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es liegt in der politischen Verantwortung der letzten Regierungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass heute nur noch eine ganz kleine Minderheit mit dem BAf\u00f6G unterst\u00fctzt wird und dass das BAf\u00f6G praktisch wirklich auf dem Weg in die v\u00f6llige Bedeutungslosigkeit ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.960", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz ehrlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schwingen sich hier immer zu gro\u00dfen Reden zum BAf\u00f6G auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das nimmt Ihnen keiner mehr ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil man dann irgendwann auch einmal etwas f\u00fcr die Ausgestaltung des BAf\u00f6G tun muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute ist es im \u00dcbrigen so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Studierenden nicht etwa durch das BAf\u00f6G am meisten unterst\u00fctzt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.880", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern dass die Eltern der Studierenden wieder den gr\u00f6\u00dften Beitrag zum Studium ihrer Kinder leisten m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den allermeisten F\u00e4llen reicht diese Unterst\u00fctzung der Eltern aber nicht aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "69\u00a0Prozent der Studierenden gehen darum neben ihrem Studium einer Erwerbsarbeit nach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.600", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist der h\u00f6chste Wert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.600", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der jemals gemessen wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die zwei Tage pro Woche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Studierende arbeiten gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fehlen nat\u00fcrlich f\u00fcr das Studium und verl\u00e4ngern die Studienzeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist v\u00f6llig widersinnig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar nicht nur f\u00fcr die Studierenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.160", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch f\u00fcr die Hochschulen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir in diesen Tagen \u00fcber das BAf\u00f6G reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann es doch nicht mehr nur um ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zwei kleine Anpassungen gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.680", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern dann muss es um eine Reform gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wirklich das Potenzial hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das BAf\u00f6G seine urspr\u00fcnglichen Zwecke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich \u201eBildungsbeteiligung in der Breite\u201c und \u201eSozialer Aufstieg\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.160", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder erf\u00fcllen kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.880", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum muss es hier heute doch gehen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen dem Antrag der Gr\u00fcnen zustimmen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn im Gegensatz zur Regierung kommt von den Gr\u00fcnen wenigstens etwas."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber eines ist doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ehrlich gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.600", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wohl auch klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Vorschl\u00e4ge im Gr\u00fcnen-Antrag reichen nicht aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.920", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Probleme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in dem Antrag angesprochen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wirklich zu l\u00f6sen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen eine substanzielle und nachhaltige BAf\u00f6G-Reform. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alles andere wird den Bedeutungsverlust des BAf\u00f6G nicht stoppen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.200", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Richtig peinlich fand ich die Ank\u00fcndigung der neuen GroKo, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man wolle beim BAf\u00f6G bis 2021 zu einer Trendumkehr kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2021! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist irre! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit hat die Gro\u00dfe Koalition eigentlich angek\u00fcndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.400", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich in ihrer Regierungszeit gar nichts ver\u00e4ndern wird\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das auf Kosten von Zehntausenden jungen Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die aus Geldgr\u00fcnden auf die Erf\u00fcllung ihres Studienwunsches verzichten m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist Wahnsinn!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.360", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Linke sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.360", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen eine gro\u00dfe Reform des BAf\u00f6G, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bedeutet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.480", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Bildung nicht mehr vom Geldbeutel der Eltern abh\u00e4ngt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die dazu beitr\u00e4gt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die soziale Spaltung in diesem Land zu beenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.480", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das und nichts Geringeres ist die Aufgabe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.000", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu ihrer ersten Rede im Deutschen Bundestag erh\u00e4lt die Abgeordnete Katrin Staffler aus der CDU/CSU-Fraktion das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}